    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "三种都要支持。Ollama用于本地开发和隐私敏感场景，Claude和OpenAI用于生产环境的高性能需求。这些应该作为外部系统放在图的外围。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ollama",
        "Claude API",
        "OpenAI API"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把Azure DevOps、GitHub、Ollama、Claude API、OpenAI API都作为外部软件系统放在外层。现在开始构建核心的AI Code Agent容器组。",
